OL,3,CBarry Hills remembered as 'one of the
OL,4,Cgreats' as his death is announced
OL,6,FAngus Gold described Barry Hills as
OL,7,F"one of the greats in my lifetime", as
OL,8,Fhe joined the racing community in
OL,9,Fpaying tribute to the training great
OL,10,Ffollowing his death at the age of 88.
OL,12,FHills, who lived in Lambourn,
OL,13,FBerkshire sent out over 3,000 winners
OL,14,Fthroughout his career, with many
OL,15,Fcoming in the colours of Sheikh Hamdan
OL,16,FAl Maktoum's Shadwell operation, whom
OL,17,Fhis son Richard Hills rode as retained
OL,18,Frider for during a large portion of
OL,19,Fhis career.
