OL,3,CBarry Hills remembered as 'one of the
OL,4,Cgreats' as his death is announced
OL,6,FFather and son joined forces to win
OL,7,Fthe 2000 Guineas with Haafhd in 2004,
OL,8,Fwhile five years later they added the
OL,9,F1000 Guineas in unison thanks to
OL,10,FGhanaati, with Shadwell's long-serving
OL,11,Fracing manager Gold hailing Hills'
OL,12,Fdedication to his craft following many
OL,13,Fyears spent in the upper echelons of
OL,14,Fthe training ranks.
OL,16,FHe said, "For many, many years we were
OL,17,Flucky enough to have horses with him
OL,18,Fand what a great man, you don't need
OL,19,Fme to tell you the success he made of
OL,20,Fhis life and career.
