OL,3,CBarry Hills remembered as 'one of the
OL,4,Cgreats' as his death is announced
OL,6,F"He was a great trainer who was
OL,7,Ftotally dedicated and lived for the
OL,8,Fsport. He was an incredibly shrewd man
OL,9,Fand a great judge of a horse and their
OL,10,Fcapabilities from just watching them
OL,11,Fon the gallops.
OL,13,F"He was a fascinating man to be with
OL,14,Fand great fun. He was one of the
OL,15,Fgreats in my lifetime and I learned a
OL,16,Flot from him and even a month ago he
OL,17,Fwas spotting things out on the gallops
OL,18,Fand still loved it even though he had
OL,19,Fgiven up the licence."
