OL,3,CBarry Hills remembered as 'one of the
OL,4,Cgreats' as his death is announced
OL,6,FHills announced his retirement in
OL,7,FAugust 2011 after overcoming serious
OL,8,Fillnesses, including throat cancer,
OL,9,Fbut he did make a brief return to
OL,10,Ftraining on a temporary licence in
OL,11,F2014, before returning to background
OL,12,Fat the family's Faringdon Place yard.
OL,14,FHowever, as the head of a dynasty that
OL,15,Fis still influential in racing, his
OL,16,Fname will live on through the exploits
OL,17,Fof his sons, with Charlie Hills now
OL,18,Fcontinuing the Group One success
OL,19,Fsynonymous with the famous Lambourn
OL,20,Foperation.
