OL,3,CBarry Hills remembered as 'one of the
OL,4,Cgreats' as his death is announced
OL,6,F"He was a remarkable man and we were
OL,7,Flucky to have him for so long, he was
OL,8,Fso tough," continued Gold.
OL,10,F"He had been ill on and off for so
OL,11,Flong, it was just incredible his will
OL,12,Fto live and enthusiasm for life, a
OL,13,Ftruly wonderful man.
