OL,3,CBarry Hills remembered as 'one of the
OL,4,Cgreats' as his death is announced
OL,6,F"All five boys were heavily involved.
OL,7,FSadly John died and then you've the
OL,8,Ftwins (Richard and Michael) who
OL,9,Feveryone obviously know all about and
OL,10,Fthen there's Charlie who trains and
OL,11,FGeorge who is making a fine career out
OL,12,Fin America, so it is a dynasty that
OL,13,Fwill live on, there is no question
OL,14,Fabout that."
OL,16,FAmong the countless big-race winners
OL,17,Ffor Hills was Gildoran, who won the
OL,18,FAscot Gold Cup in 1984 and 1985.
