OL,3,CBarry Hills remembered as 'one of the
OL,4,Cgreats' as his death is announced
OL,6,FThe track said on X: "Everybody at
OL,7,FAscot Racecourse is saddened to hear
OL,8,Fabout the death of Barry Hills. We
OL,9,Fsend all our condolences to his
OL,10,Ffriends and family at this time.
OL,12,F"Barry enjoyed huge success at Ascot
OL,13,Fand Royal Ascot including with the
OL,14,Flikes of Gildoran who was a dual Gold
OL,15,FCup winner and Sure Blade who won the
OL,16,FCoventry Stakes, St James's Palace
OL,17,FStakes and Queen Elizabeth II Stakes."
