OL,6,FIn similar vein, officials at York
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our thoughts and prayers are
OL,8,Fwith the Hills family. Barry had so
OL,9,Fmany highlights on the Knavesmire, be
OL,10,Fit Handsome Sailor in the Coolmore
OL,11,FNunthorpe, Royal Applause in the Al
OL,12,FBasti Equiworld Gimcrack or Further
OL,13,FFlight landing him a Sky Bet Ebor `
OL,14,FRest in Peace."
OL,16,FThe Racehorse Owners Association said:
OL,17,F"Everyone at the ROA is deeply
OL,18,Fsaddened by the passing of Barry
OL,19,FHills, and we extend our heartfelt
OL,20,Fcondolences to his family and friends
OL,21,Fduring this time.
